# Gomoku - Environment Variables Template

## Backend (.env in backend/)
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@host:5432/gomoku?schema=public"
JWT_SECRET="at-least-32-random-characters-here"
JWT_EXPIRES_IN="7d"
PORT=4000
CORS_ORIGIN="https://gomoku.vercel.app"

## Frontend (.env in frontend/)
VITE_API_URL="https://gomoku-api.railway.app"
